{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f90e357c93","title":"关于国共谈判情况及我们的原则立场致张学良电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a2d8afb3d4","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":10,"articleId":"f90e357c93"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"29c32210cc","type":"paragraph","text":"关于国共谈判情况及我们的原则立场","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f90e357c93"},{"id":"6da8b8b072","type":"paragraph","text":"致张学良电","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f90e357c93"},{"id":"99248448fc","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月10日）李宜兄：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f90e357c93"},{"id":"8a616a583a","type":"paragraph","text":"（甲）雨苍已动身，删日可抵兄处","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f90e357c93"},{"id":"33e566e799","type":"paragraph","text":"（乙）陈立夫第三次找汉年谈，红军留三方，服从南京，要我方让步。我们复称根本不同意蒋氏对外妥协、对内黄求之政策，更根本拒绝其悔唇红军之态度。红军仅可在抗日救亡之前提下承认改换抗日番号，划定抗日防地，服从抗日指挥，不能减少一兵一萃，并须扩充之。彼方如有诚意，须立即停战，并退出苏区以外，静待谈判结果。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f90e357c93"},{"id":"93be1f5af4","type":"paragraph","text":"（丙）我们决心以战争求和平，绝对不作无原则让步。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f90e357c93"},{"id":"80e9cdb844","type":"paragraph","text":"（丁）因上海电台尚未建立，暂时不得不由兄转，今有一要电致汉年，祈赐转为荷。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f90e357c93"},{"id":"f70817c820","type":"paragraph","text":"弟东来","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f90e357c93"},{"id":"023b809cc8","type":"paragraph","text":"蒸申[1]指叶剑英。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f90e357c93"}],"page":{"id":"e52ca196ff","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"f90e357c93","start":151,"end":151}}}},"__N_SSG":true}